    "description": "体验古怪而混乱的游戏玩法，其中可爱的摇摇晃晃的笨蛋们在高速的淘汰赛场景中战斗。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2342290/extras/a7472b2a2f9aa38d637ccf4aa1eb0c2c.poster.avif?t=1734037513\" width=800 height=222 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2342290/extras/a7472b2a2f9aa38d637ccf4aa1eb0c2c.webm?t=1734037513\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2342290/extras/a7472b2a2f9aa38d637ccf4aa1eb0c2c.mp4?t=1734037513\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>《橡皮大逃杀》（Rubber Royale）容易上手和学习。只需加入游戏，自定义你的角色，并与陌生人或朋友在各种不同的游戏模式中战斗，最后站立的人成为胜利者，这是一个疯狂的王者盛宴。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2342290/extras/dfaf9b8654922a47735bbe1903012660.poster.avif?t=1734037513\" width=370 height=38 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2342290/extras/dfaf9b8654922a47735bbe1903012660.webm?t=1734037513\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2342290/extras/dfaf9b8654922a47735bbe1903012660.mp4?t=1734037513\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>16名玩家<br></li><li>即时动作<br></li><li>大型、可破坏、酷炫的竞技场<br></li><li>全新武器库，包括许多你最喜欢的《橡胶强盗》（Rubber Bandits）中的武器<br></li><li>淘汰赛、王者之王、竞速等经典游戏模式，以及更多！</li></ul><br>但请注意。这是那种让你在最后一刻被你最好的朋友扔过卫生纸，让你跌倒在终点线前，无法晋级下一轮，然后对着他大喊大叫的游戏。所以准备好试着向愤怒的朋友道歉，同时忍住笑泪。<br><br>傻乎乎、令人上瘾和混乱的乐趣等着你。",
